{"tid":1673164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"叫foodpanda撞到前度","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T10:25:28.000Z","uid":209657,"like":40,"dislike":392,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4e63b3ec76d0c3576fe065a4050cc2ea1da8a5","tid":1673164,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"我頭先同男朋友喺屋企肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到foodpanda有discount 就諗住嗌黎食<br />\norder完之後發現 車手個名竟然同我ex一樣！<br />\n嚇到我心都離一離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻入房換返件喱士睡衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個app彈左通知話就到<br />\n我就叫我bb一陣開門攞外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叮咚～～<br />\n我偷偷喺我bb後面望一望隻熊貓仔<br />\n原來真係我前度！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就即刻攬住我bb話：咦bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />～～有野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />～～～俾d tips人地啦 你睇下佢幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再掃視左我ex身水身汗個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後轉身 俾左個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">差評</span>佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4d6f857be3236b0e6f39e5ddd88eef8f513f47","tid":1673164,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=26f59c29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d200929bb6ec7b3f08379fa3111f4b4c5e9e117a","tid":1673164,"uid":31370,"